messages.message: I wonder if we should also include a copyable App name, in addition to a copyable App ID, for ease of running an app by name or ID? It would be nice to just have both options in the same place and easy to copy--I can see users wondering if they need to include spaces etc when writing out the app name in the API param.
I think what we really need actually is auto-generated API code :smile: - copyable API parameters should really be a short term fix
